*   2010 *[The Eerie Silence](/The_Eerie_Silence)*, Houghton Mifflin Harcourt, [ISBN](/ISBN_(identifier)) 1-4001-6551-2. A reflection on the Fermi paradox and the persistent lack of observable extraterrestrial intelligence, a silence that often speaks volumes.
